{"tid":1976681,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[整滑鼠]G402維修","createTime":"2020-04-17T11:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T13:49:48.000Z","uid":52656,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"63309c9fad94a0181c7d51ebab8cfcc53ad3e79e","tid":1976681,"uid":52656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T11:36:42.000Z","msg":"由於之前賣左隻G402滑鼠比朋友<br />\n已經換哂新殼,不過之前用落都OK<br />\n咁我換完就比佢<br />\n大約過左半年左右<br />\n佢話滾輪中間粒制係拉落既時候會係咁HI到<br />\n叫我睇下<br />\n於是就拆開左<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/17/qStKay.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F17%2FqStKay.jpg&h=07f1b776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而我發覺果然係中間粒野壞左<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/17/mbA5CT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F17%2FmbA5CT.jpg&h=d9095deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於呢D制比較少<br />\n好彩之前屎忽痕見平買左幾粒看門口,順便換埋左右制,佢最緊要耐用,所以換左2粒聲稱5000萬次既D2FC-F-K(50M)<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/17/1idbHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F17%2F1idbHz.jpg&h=f9012772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n換完之後測試,再拍片比佢睇,收工<br />\n由於太急冇影事後<br />\n搵到之前整其中一隻SENSEI RAW 既相<br />\n換左靜音同埋新殼新線<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/17/qnyTJN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F17%2FqnyTJN.jpg&h=1fea51e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/17/75h0jo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F17%2F75h0jo.jpg&h=4f32befa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實整呢D MOUSE好簡單,而且成本都好平 <br />\n不過考驗大家動手能力<br />\n志在分享下,我知呢道大把高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},